OL,6,FRail passengers are being shown how
OL,7,Foften trains are cancelled and delayed
OL,8,Fat individual stations for the first
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,12,Fsaid the policy heralds "a new era of
OL,13,Frail accountability".
OL,15,FPerformance data produced by regulator
OL,16,Fthe Office of Rail and Road is now
OL,17,Favailable for more than 1,700 stations.
