OL,3,CTrain passengers to be shown how often
OL,4,Ctrains are cancelled and delayed
OL,6,FDigital screens at major stations are
OL,7,Fdisplaying the statistics, while the
OL,8,Finformation for smaller stations is
OL,9,Favailable to view online by scanning
OL,10,FQR codes.
OL,12,FThe screens also provide information
OL,13,Fon work operators and Network Rail are
OL,14,Fdoing in their area to improve
OL,15,Fperformance.
OL,17,FTrain reliability across Britain is at
OL,18,Fa record low, with the equivalent of
OL,19,Fmore than one in 25 services cancelled
OL,20,Fin the year to February 1.
