OL,6,FMs Alexander said: "Today marks the
OL,7,Fbeginning of a new era of rail
OL,8,Faccountability.
OL,10,F"These displays are a step towards
OL,11,Frebuilding trust with passengers using
OL,12,Four railways, as we continue to tackle
OL,13,Fthe root causes of frustrating delays
OL,14,Fand cancellations.
OL,16,F"Through fundamental rail reform,
OL,17,Fwe're sweeping away decades of
OL,18,Fdysfunctionality ` putting passengers
OL,19,Ffirst, driving growth through
OL,20,Fconnectivity as part of this
OL,21,FGovernment's Plan for Change."
