OL,3,CTrain passengers to be shown how often
OL,4,Ctrains are cancelled and delayed
OL,6,FData is available for the 14 operators
OL,7,Ffunded by the Department for Transport
OL,8,F(DfT), as well as for other train
OL,9,Fcompanies who have agreed it can be
OL,10,Fdisplayed.
OL,12,FAnalysis by the PA news agency found
OL,13,FEaling Broadway in west London was the
OL,14,Fmajor station with the worst
OL,15,Freliability of services in the four
OL,16,Fweeks to February 1.
OL,18,FThat is out of the 77 stations with
OL,19,Fmore than 10,000 scheduled services in
OL,20,Fthat period.
