OL,4,Ctrains are cancelled and delayed
OL,6,FThe equivalent of 7.9% of services at
OL,7,FEaling Broadway ` which is used by
OL,8,FElizabeth line and Great Western
OL,9,FRailway trains ` were cancelled.
OL,11,FElizabeth line stations make up seven
OL,12,Fof the 10 worst for cancellations,
OL,13,Fincluding Bond Street (7.4%),
OL,14,FFarringdon (6.5%) and Paddington
OL,15,F(5.6%).
OL,17,FThe other three stations are all on
OL,18,FMerseyside's Merseyrail network, which
OL,19,Fhas suffered problems with trains
OL,20,Fbeing unable to draw electricity from
OL,21,Fthe third rail during wintry weather.
