OL,6,FThe highest cancellation score of any
OL,7,Fstation in England was 22.8% at Ince &
OL,8,FElton in Cheshire, which is one of the
OL,9,Fleast used in the country.
OL,11,FIt was scheduled to have just 92
OL,12,Fservices during the period.
OL,14,FJacqueline Starr, chief executive of
OL,15,Fthe Rail Delivery Group, which
OL,16,Frepresents operators, said: "We know
OL,17,Fhow frustrating it is for customers
OL,18,Fwhen their train is cancelled or
OL,19,Fdelayed.
