OL,6,F"By being transparent with this data
OL,7,Fand the positive actions we're taking,
OL,8,Fit shows how serious the industry is
OL,9,Fin putting this right by continuing to
OL,10,Fstrive for improvements.
OL,12,F"This send a clear message to
OL,13,Fcustomers the rail sector is committed
OL,14,Fto improving punctuality and to find
OL,15,Fsolutions to make train services more
OL,16,Freliable."
