OL,6,FNatasha Grice, director at watchdog
OL,7,FTransport Focus, said: "Passengers
OL,8,Ftell us they want a reliable, on-time
OL,9,Ftrain service and will welcome
OL,10,Fimprovements to information about the
OL,11,Fpunctuality of their service and
OL,12,Fcancellations being shared more
OL,13,Ftransparently.
OL,15,F"It's important that the industry uses
OL,16,Fthis information to drive up
OL,17,Fperformance."
OL,19,FThe DfT is consulting on proposals for
OL,20,Fhow Great British Railways will run.
